Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.53,0:00:52.80,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}kururu  kururu  ku  把足跡畫上×
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.26,0:00:59.68,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}穿過校舍的牆壁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:07.96,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}通向四方的路  就在腳下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:15.24,OPC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)}裙子的摺痕是不會亂的
